/group><group invisible="not hide_use_payment_terminal or type != 'bank'"><div colspan="2"><h2>Tips:</h2><p>Go to<a class="btn-link o_form_uri" href="#" name="533" role="button" type="action">Configurations &gt; Settings</a><strong>&gt; Payment Terminals</strong>in order to install a Payment Terminal and make a fully integrated payment method.</p></div></group><group invisible="hide_use_payment_terminal"><field name="use_payment_terminal"></field></group></group></sheet></form>